  "title": "Operating Theatre Technician",
  "description": "<p><strong>The Opportunity:</strong></p><p>We are looking for individuals to deliver safe and quality activities in the Perioperative Services.</p><p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><p>Operating Theatre:</p><ul><li>Maintain cleanliness of OTs before and after surgeries</li><li>Assist nursing team to prepare necessary equipment for procedures.</li><li>Assist nursing team in OT during procedure in progress.</li></ul><p>Endoscopy Room:</p><ul><li>Maintain cleanliness of Endo room.</li><li>Assist nursing team when procedure in progress.</li><li>Assist nursing team in reprocessing of scopes.</li></ul><p>Theatre Sterile Service Unit:</p><ul><li>Maintain cleanliness of the sterilisation room.</li><li>Assist nursing team in washing, drying, packing and sterilisation of instruments and packs.</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum GCE \"N\" / \"O\" Level or equivalent</li><li>Candidate with relevant experience or with WSQ Higher Certificate in Healthcare Support (Operating Theatre) preferred Comfortable with patient contact</li><li>Position and salary will commensurate with past relevant experience</li></ul>",
